ionios F.C.|Panionios]]\n| [[Athens]]\n| [[Nea Smyrni Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 11,700\n|-\n| [[Panthrakikos F.C.|Panthrakikos]]\n| [[Komotini]]\n| [[Komotini Municipal Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 6,500\n|-\n| [[PAOK FC|PAOK]]\n| [[Thessaloniki]]\n| [[Toumba Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 28,701\n|-\n| [[Xanthi F.C.|Skoda Xanthi]]\n| [[Xanthi]]\n| [[Skoda Xanthi Arena]]\n| align=\"center\" | 7,361\n|}\n\n===Personnel and sponsoring===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Club\n! Manager <!--The term is similar to head coach-->\n! Kit maker\n! Shirt sponsor\n|-\n| [[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]\n| {{flagicon|Bosnia-Herzegovina}} [[Du\u0161an Bajevi\u0107]]\n| [[Puma AG|Puma]]\n| [[Diners Club]]\n|-\n| [[Aris Thessaloniki F.C.|Aris]]\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[H\u00e9ctor C\u00faper]]\n| [[Reebok]]\n| [[EKO Refineries|EKO]]\n|-\n| [[Asteras Tripoli F.C.|Asteras Tripoli]]\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Roberto Carlos Mario G\u00f3mez|Mario G\u00f3mez]]\n| [[Lotto Sport Italia|Lotto]]\n| [[OPAP]]\n|-\n| [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]\n| {{flagicon|Greece}} [[Giorgos Donis]]\n| [[ASICS|Asics]]\n| [[OPAP]]\n|-\n| [[Ergotelis F.C.|Ergotelis]]\n| {{flagicon|Greece}} [[Nikos Karageorgiou]]\n| [[Lotto Sport Italia|Lotto]]\n| [[OPAP]]\n|-\n| [[Iraklis 1908 Thessaloniki F.C.|Iraklis]]\n| {{flagicon|Slovakia}} [[Jozef Bubenko]]\n| [[Puma AG|Puma]]\n| [[Bank of Attica|Attica bank]]\n|-\n| [[Kavala F.C.|Kavala]]\n| {{flagicon|Netherlands}} [[Aad de Mos]]\n| [[Puma AG|Puma]]\n| [[OPAP]]\n|-\n| [[AEL 1964 FC|Larissa]]\n| {{flagicon|Greece}} [[Marinos Ouzounidis]]\n| [[Adidas]]\n| [[On Telecoms]]\n|-\n| [[Levadiakos F.C.|Levadiakos]]\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Quique Hern\u00e1ndez]]\n| [[Puma AG|Puma]]\n| [[OPAP]]\n|-\n| [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n| {{flagicon|Serbia}} [[Bo\u017eidar Bandovi\u0107]]\n| [[Puma AG|Puma]]\n| [[Citibank]]\n|-\n| [[Panathinaikos F.C.|Panathinaikos]]\n| {{flagicon|Greece}} [[Nikos Nioplias]]\n| [[Adidas]]\n| [[Cosmote]]\n|-\n| [[Panionios F.C.